row-text: The Day You and I Started Loving Each Other
kyniem-top: 1 Month Anniversary of You and Me Loving Each Other
kyniem-text1: So officially you and I have been together for a full month, and I thank you for coming to me and always being by my side, Forever My Girl <3<3
kyniem-text2: With each passing day, our love grows a little more. Congratulations on our 1 month love anniversary. I hope you will continue the journey ahead with me. I love you, my lovely Girl ♥ ♥ ♥
